subSubSection.paragraph:
Operculum semicircular; dorsal and lateral margins well developed, smooth; ventral margin (opercular ridge) with 10–13 pairs of golden paleae (
holotype
13 pairs), curved dorsally, acute with extended tips (
Figs 31E–F
; 
32A–B
; 
33B–C
).

